    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong> &quot;Dear Gretel. Let's meet again after three nights. You have to be a nice girl. - Mom and Dad &quot;</strong></i></h2><br><br>Little girl Gretel heads to Madame Winslow's Mansion on an errand from her parents.<br>The note given by her parents says that they will pick her up after three nights.<br>Now Gretel stays at Madame Winslow's Mansion and helps her with her work for three days.<br><br>But<br>The Mansion, Madame Winslow, and Gilbert the butler,<br>They seem to be hiding something behind a friendly attitude.<br><br>Look into objects and get items.<br>Solve the puzzle properly and find out the secret of the mansion.<br><br>Will Gretel be able to return safely to her parents' arms after three days?<br><br><strong>Explore the mansion, collect objects, and solve the puzzles.</strong><br>Madame Winslow's Mansion has several rooms.<br>Look into the rooms to follow the given to-do list. Click to get the required items, and accomplish the missions.<br>Of course, it depends on your choice <i>'How'</i> you will accomplish what you have to do. Follow the advice.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767320/extras/description_image1.png?t=1767106962\" /></span><br><br><strong>Find out the Truth and collect the endings.</strong><br>Follow the story and make appropriate choices in various branches. Depending on your choices, you can have a total of 4 different endings.<br>Please help Gretel go home safely and have a happy ending.<br>Simply getting out of the mansion is not the end of everything. Be careful always.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767320/extras/description_image2.png?t=1767106962\" /></span>",
